definitions.definition: A closed loop or eyelet at one end of a lariat or lasso , through which the other end of the rope is passed to form a much larger loop.
A grommet or other device intended to strengthen or otherwise improve a simple rope honda.

main_definition: ( Southwestern US ) A closed loop or eyelet at one end of a lariat or lasso , through which the other end of the rope is passed to form a much larger loop.
